  "texts": [
    "Finally, the participants were sent an optional feedback survey after the deliberation.",
    "Feedback from participants is described in Appendix A. 3.",
    "As mentioned, we conducted two sessions per demographic group.",
    "The only difference between these two sessions, other than the participants themselves, was that in the first session, time was reserved to ask participants \"what's missing from the themes in these samples, based on your experience?\"",
    "The goal of this question was to fill any gaps in the themes offered by the toxic speech experts described in Stage 1 with themes the participants felt might be missing."
  ],
